Isn't it great to feel strong, active and healthy? Isn’t it great to feel strong, active and healthy? A healthy body and mind means quality of life!
This wearable offers you applications to help you stay fit. It is designed to support you during the day and render peace in the evening. It helps increase your vitality to improve the flow of your energy reserves. This wearable has been cleared by the U.S. Food and Drug Administration. 
For more information contact Annacabanna at 615-412-9774.
You can pause and play by saying "Alexa, pause" and "Alexa, resume." Just say "Alexa, stop" when you're done for the day. When listening to podcasts you can say "Alexa, shuffle" to shuffle the playing order, or "Alexa, loop" to loop the current episode. You can also ask for previous and next episodes by saying "Alexa, previous" and "Alexa, next". Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
